parameters: '体制に反抗せよ！怪人レジスタンス結成！！の巻'
'大首領様と作戦会議しよう！'

Bunny-chan: Ugh... I wonder if Memimi-chan saw the
message... I hope she managed to escape...

Brachiocondor: She's tough, no matter what. She'll manage...
Right, Shark Broccoli?

Shark Broccoli: Now that I've lost my broccoli, I'm just a
shark... I don't know what future the Orca Duke will
choose... but if worst comes to worst, I could always
surrender to Mayor Orca Asparagus...

Brachiocondor: Please, spare me that... After that orca
bastard stormed into the Monster Fight, almost all the
organizations in the city got scared and disbanded.

Bunny-chan: If you get on the mayor's bad side, you can't
even walk around the city anymore. And now, if the only
leader who stood up to him, Shark Broccoli-san, bows his
head... it's as good as a complete defeat for all the
monsters in the city...

Anomalocaris: Are we finished then? The underlings of our
organization have been hunted by the mayor or left the
city... There are only a few of us left with any spirit.

Cerberus Octopus: Even so, sucking up to the mayor now won't
get us any good positions. As retaliation for letting the
big boss escape, they've crushed all our operations... If
there's no plan for a big comeback, we're just slowly dying
out... Huh?

Memimi: Everyone...! Are you all right...? I'm sorry, it's
my fault for losing... The message saved me... Thanks to it,
I'm here...

Shark Broccoli: You've returned well, Orca Duke... I've
caused you pain... Thanks to you, we were saved.

Memimi: You flatter me too much, great leader-sama...! To
see you in such a pitiable state... I must retrieve the
broccoli from him at all costs and repair your monster
suit...

Bunny-chan: Memimi-chan...! You saw the message, didn't
you—thank goodness! I was so worried about you.

Memimi: Bunny-chan...! Thank you... I really owe you one...
Ugh... It was really... dangerous...

Brachiocondor: Looks like you haven't lost your fangs yet!
That's the woman who defeated me... Here, have some orange
juice.

Memimi: It's a calming taste... Thank you, Brachiocondor. If
I were to break over something like this, it would cause
trouble for you too since you lost to me...

Anomalocaris: Mosmos... Could it be that the tide is turning
in our favor? The Orca Duke is still kicking!

Cerberus Octopus: Just having her around makes it feel like
things will go well...! Having fought her myself, I know
that this girl's potential is higher than any other monster
in the city!!

Memimi has successfully reunited with her scattered
comrades...!
